Cookbook:

Vaulted Variables:
ansible-vault edit unmentionables.yml --vault-password-file ~/.ansible_vault_pass

Code deploy:
ansible-playbook -i hosts deploy.yml --tags push --vault-password-file ~/.ansible_vault_pass

Server Config deploy:
ansible-playbook -i hosts deploy.yml --vault-password-file ~/.ansible_vault_pass

Server Provision
ansible-playbook -i hosts provision.yml --vault-password-file ~/.ansible_vault_pass
